{"id": 2853, "genre": 1000, "title": "你对自己未来的老年生活都有哪些野生养老思路？", "description": "低结婚率和出生率的未来里，依靠政府和下一代养老的可能性有多大？也许既没有配偶也没有子女的我们，是时候想想老年生活了（欢迎在留言区补充）。", "record_count": 17582, "comment_count": 86, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190319151043AwUGBY41OfKTZELu.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-19T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5538, "title": "你对自己未来的老年生活都有哪些野生养老思路？", "content": "你对自己未来的老年生活都有哪些野生养老思路？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 333930, "content": "生孩子，和家人一起共度晚年", "image": "img/option/option/201903191517308cp2vd7nUG0lxDkP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 333931, "content": "养儿防老是没戏了，希望能挤进好点的养老院", "image": "img/option/option/20190319151800UpT3FhBnxyICzqZm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 333932, "content": "和一堆老朋友合租在别墅/公寓里", "image": "img/option/option/20190319151852YZhOAqvzXTM5x7K8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 333934, "content": "但求猫狗双全，只有猫也行", "image": "img/option/option/20190319152027WJpbya8ITA7wogYK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 333935, "content": "保持锻炼健康饮食，节省医疗护理费", "image": "img/option/option/20190319152116A2CX6jZOerIx04Ei.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 333937, "content": "移民到社保体系更完善的国家去", "image": "img/option/option/201903191522414vqxXN95n2sOPAIQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 333938, "content": "期望科技发展快些，有机器人能来养老", "image": "img/option/option/20190319152455ZFS6iNMECBbWe35q.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 333941, "content": "年轻时就开始为养老买保险金", "image": "img/option/option/20190319152750wbhKL0SpRjE4ZykH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 333940, "content": "养啥老，已经做好工作到死的打算", "image": "img/option/option/20190319152613quMCcDOrYWA0oh15.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}